snippet.title: Best VGM 1663 - Midnight Resistance - Flood of Power (Stage 1)
snippet.description:
A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Genesis
Midnight Resistance
Flood of Power (Stage 1)
Azusa Hara, Hiroaki Yoshida, Tatsuya Kiuchi, Hitomi Komatsu & Fuse
